{"tid":1435633,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我就係大台！有錯既！入嚟屌柒我。","createTime":"2019-08-09T06:01:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T06:19:24.000Z","uid":203413,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4c7a56123d006e99091644aeb3b711b348f76105","tid":1435633,"uid":203413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:01:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">邊撚個話只可以有一個大台？我都有一個一人大台嫁！！！果個大台就係我自己！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你起左大台，無問題。唔一定有人聽，我地只會繼續「五大訴求，缺一不可」。所謂大台舉行既活動，係岩既我就會參加，唔岩既我就繼續爬山。你同政府妥協既，好！無問題！係代表你既大台。<br />\n<br />\n你完左，我想要既仲味得到，我只會同以往一樣，繼續上街做我地要做既野！所以我根本唔需要理有無大台。有同無都係一撚樣。「五大訴求，缺一不可」。<br />\n<br />\n如果你覺得你已經得到你想要既，你可以落車，但我地仍然係有同一信念既隊友。如果你發現你想要更多，隨時可以上車，開往自由既車門一直為你而開。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化、勿捉鬼、不篤灰、不抹黑、不割蓆</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>兄弟爬山，各自努力。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我就係大台！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求，<br />\n缺一不可。</span>"},{"pid":"11fdb5da2177168470be4809f43459d1d488a864","tid":1435633,"uid":203413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:03:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>五大訴求，<br />\n缺一不可。</strong></span>"},{"pid":"eeb2498f4314c43565305981fadb11c91151ae66","tid":1435633,"uid":284104,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:04:01.000Z","msg":"人人都係自己既大台<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8a02a3c2e03070e8ef23bde36c3560da30ac6fa","tid":1435633,"uid":203413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:04:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我就係大台！</strong></span>"},{"pid":"0d456d0a81ce5c305a3a9e11fc197b5144f0ee7b","tid":1435633,"uid":203413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eeb2498f4314c43565305981fadb11c91151ae66","tid":1435633,"uid":284104,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:04:01.000Z","msg":"人人都係自己既大台<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:05:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n要談判就同每一個香港人講！<br />\n</strong></span>"},{"pid":"53dc654dd96d8012d534ac60056a693ee242a5a6","tid":1435633,"uid":203413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:05:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力。<br />\n</strong></span>"},{"pid":"61f35106545c9116870ffe6e2e660088f4f86fe7","tid":1435633,"uid":203413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:07:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n不分化<br />\n</strong></span>"},{"pid":"bd5a44724cdc14bdfe0d2b70bd275ad0f03d4020","tid":1435633,"uid":276191,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:07:35.000Z","msg":"一人一個大台<br />\n唔該政府同哂咁多個大台傾至好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61f2c42e46a4d1ce867b942baef50abb2d041705","tid":1435633,"uid":203413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:07:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n勿捉鬼<br />\n</strong></span>"},{"pid":"39921c2cfa3c67a965606a947f8f78a70b9bc9d3","tid":1435633,"uid":203413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd5a44724cdc14bdfe0d2b70bd275ad0f03d4020","tid":1435633,"uid":276191,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:07:35.000Z","msg":"一人一個大台<br />\n唔該政府同哂咁多個大台傾至好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:09:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n無錯！要妥協既！一個一個嚟！<br />\n</strong></span>"},{"pid":"fd15327e2a8c2e82b01348e858fd629fd8239c29","